news.title: Goa's IT department takes step towards drawing up policy for co-working spaces
news.para: Khaunte said that DoIT has already identified land at Morjim, Caranzalem and Benaulim where the three co-working spaces will come up on the beach.

news.title: Mumbai: With nowhere to go, residents stay put in unsafe buildings
news.para: Before the monsoon this year, the BMC declared 337 residential buildings in Mumbai dangerous. Civic officials said that out of these buildings, 163 are in the western suburbs, 104 are in the eastern suburbs, wherein 70 buildings are in the island city.

news.title: Delhi civic body starts tendering process for digitising 10,000 properties
news.para: Officials said that the hard copy/original documents of some of these properties are lying in a deplorable state and their digitisation is a must for future reference.
